知道英國在撤退殖民地時給當地人英籍，不論有居留權與否，都有留有一手，甚至有太平門的味道。林鄭應知道她幫助中國倒行逆施，已經實際上觸動了BNO平權的界線，才會反應如此強烈。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180123/20282780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180123%2F20282780&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=504858fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180123%2F20282780&h=f0bec490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180123/20282780</a>"},{"pid":"0c3a73457a8741889cfa3986d21cde2630e4b6f1","tid":2073501,"uid":342893,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4hQaZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4hQaZg.jpg&h=216cedea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"042dcac996abe81750056f3d89f7ef1a660a0f50","tid":2073501,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"487ee14ac034bf3b4e8fb667b267af421e1b553e","tid":2073501,"uid":24339,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"b8c74e8641e8ea81c470fa98a6a491af9180b022","tid":2073501,"uid":51583,"like":99,"dislike":1,"score":98,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"咁難明既句野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:28:01.000Z","msg":"隻隻字都識，但唔明點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"咁你要習慣下，因為BNO 香港人只會留係香港學習中國中文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fabc683abc1b6daa3efd8e16f0b6febac830305","tid":2073501,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"on99 不推文左"},{"pid":"c9a9624bc741fec7aa0931c1c64c5d4a68e3ded6","tid":2073501,"uid":146917,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"英國話會比 但係唔會直接BC <br />\